For java program:

Install javac
	sudo apt-get install gcj-4.6-jdk

Compile
	javac HelloWorldApp.java

Run
	java HelloWorldApp


******************************************************

For applet:

Compile
	javac HelloWorldApplet.java

Run
	appletviewer example.html 
	firefox example.html (under Windows, my Linux firefox has something wrong to run this applet)
